OL,5,G1130 Prue Leith's Cotswold Kitchen
OL,6,     FPrue is joined by The Great
OL,7,     FBritish Sewing Bee judge Patrick
OL,8,     FGrant, who makes a slow-cooked
OL,9,     Ffenugreek lamb dish and reveals
OL,10,     Fhow he inherited his love of
OL,11,     Fcooking from his dad. A no-knead
OL,12,     Ffocaccia is also on the menu for
OL,13,     FPrue, who explains that it takes a
OL,14,     Fbit of patience but is well worth
OL,15,     Fthe wait, while her husband John
OL,16,     Fbuilds a dovecote for the garden
