OL,5,G1245 Dermot's Taste of Ireland
OL,6,     FDermot O'Leary brings his journey
OL,7,     Fto a close on the surf-battered
OL,8,     Fshores of Strandhill in Co Sligo,
OL,9,     Fand meets a couple who have
OL,10,     Fbrought the bold, smoky flavours
OL,11,     Fof the Basque country to the
OL,12,     Fbeach. Joined by a host of faces
OL,13,     Fhe's met along the way, Dermot
OL,14,     Fthen cooks a proper feast of fresh
OL,15,     Fseafood, a deep, warming stew, and
OL,16,     Fa fruit dessert that carries the
OL,17,     Fsweetness of the whole journey
